Package Simulation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Fluid
    Fluid is a max instantiable object that is responsible for the fluid simulation.
    Max
    Max is a MaxObject's abstraction that provide basic stuffs for it's children.
    Particles
    Particles is a max instatiable object that is responsible for the particles system simulation.
    Simulation
    Simulation is a Max's abstraction that provide blobs system for it's children Please note that Simulation is an abstract class and each children will be an instantiable Max Object.
